      "id": 158012399914,
      "body_text": "Hi Andrew Garcia,     Please check whether the pedal has been disassembled. If this issue occurs, it may be caused by missing internal shims on both sides of the brake pedal or loose external screws on both sides. ",
      "user_id": 158000445778,
      "created_at": "2025-11-16T02:35:21Z",
      "updated_at": "2025-11-16T02:35:21Z",
      "incoming": false,
      "private": false,
      "source": 0
    },
    {
      "id": 158012425008,
