      "body_text": "Hi Andrew Garcia,     Please provide your order number. In addition, take a photo of the gap area to check if there is a washer and whether the wave washer is damaged, which may cause looseness.  We can send replacement washers to you, or you may purchase M8 washers of suitable thickness locally.",
