      "id": 158012678612,
      "body_text": "Hello What’s the suitable thickness of the m8 washers and where do the go. The wobble is unbearable.\r\nSent from my iPhone\r\n\r\n> ",
      "user_id": 158006979719,
      "created_at": "2025-11-21T03:35:38Z",
