      "source": 0
    },
    {
      "id": 158013155336,
      "body_text": "Hi Andrew Garcia,     First, remove the two M6 screws here and take off the corner piece. Install the M8 washer, then put everything back in place. Repeat the same steps on the other side. ",
      "user_id": 158000445778,
